<%- include('partials/header') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="help-box heading">
            <span class="icon">🩸</span>
            <h1 style="margin:0;">Help</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="help-box info">
            <span class="icon">💡</span>
            <div>
                <p>Welcome to the Blood Report System. Use the navigation bar to start a new test, view previous
                    reports, or get help.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="help-box step">
            <span class="icon">📝</span>
            <div>
                <h2>Step-by-step Instructions</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>New Test:</b> Click "New Test" in the navigation bar. Enter patient details, select the
                        required tests, input readings, and generate the report.</li>
                    <li><b>Previous Reports:</b> Click "Previous Reports" to view a list of all reports. Use the search
                        bar to find reports by patient name or date. Click a report to view details.</li>
                    <li><b>Help:</b> You are here! For further assistance, see below.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="help-box faq">
            <span class="icon">❓</span>
            <div>
                <h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>How do I edit a report?</b> Currently, reports cannot be edited after submission for data
                        integrity.</li>
                    <li><b>Can I download a report?</b> Yes, open a report and use the browser's print or save as PDF
                        feature.</li>
                    <li><b>Is my data secure?</b> All data is stored securely and only accessible to authorized users.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="help-box contact">
            <span class="icon">📞</span>
            <div>
                <h2>Contact Information</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Email: support@example.com</li>
                    <li>Phone: +1-800-555-1234</li>
                    <li>Live Chat: <a href="#">Start chat</a> (coming soon)</li>
                    <li>Contact Form: <a href="#">Submit a request</a> (coming soon)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="help-box troubleshoot">
            <span class="icon">🛠️</span>
            <div>
                <h2>Troubleshooting Tips</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Login issues:</b> Ensure your username and password are correct. If you forgot your password,
                        use the reset link or contact support.</li>
                    <li><b>Report not loading:</b> Refresh the page or check your internet connection. If the problem
                        persists, contact support.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="help-box info">
            <span class="icon">📄</span>
            <div>
                <h2>Documentation</h2>
                <p>Read the <a href="#">User Manual</a> for detailed documentation.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>